A single **marked comment on the ticket** holds the shared work state (the "work artifact"). It is found by the sentinel `{{artifact.sentinel}}` and updated in place — never duplicated. Shape:

```
{{artifact.sentinel}}
**TicketFlow** · status: planning|building|in-review|merged · branch: <branch> · updated: <YYYY-MM-DD>

### User stories
- [ ] US-1 <observable behavior>  (acceptance: <criterion>)
- [ ] US-2 …

### Acceptance criteria
- [ ] AC-1 …

### Plan
- [ ] T1 (US-1): <path> — <task>
- [ ] T2 (US-2): …

### PR
<filled by execute-ticket: PR url + number>

### Review verdict
<filled by review-ticket: ready | needs-changes + notes>
```
